{"tid":2348121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加快棄用澳洲鐵礦 中國擬2025前自給率達45%","createTime":"2020-12-31T13:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T03:45:09.000Z","uid":225931,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe0904812898e675224ee7decf0b033fabc089d","tid":2348121,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"中國在鐵礦石供應上仍受制澳洲，工信部31日就推動鋼鐵工業高質量發展的指導意見徵求意見，要求在2025年前，鐵金屬國內自給率達到45%以上，打造1至2個具有全球影響力和市場競爭力的海外權益鐵礦山，海外權益鐵礦佔進口礦比重超過20%，以增強鐵礦石定價話語權。<br />\n<br />\n指導意見強調，嚴禁新增鋼鐵產能同時，要打造若干家世界超大型鋼鐵企業集團以及專業化一流企業，力爭前五位鋼鐵企業產業集中度達到40%，前10位產業集中度達到60%。在創新發展上，要每年突破三至五種關鍵短板鋼鐵材料，鋼鐵短板材料比重下降到1&permil;以下，實現關鍵鋼鐵材料的自主保障。"},{"pid":"23955687fca033406393ebad91acde8dc1674845","tid":2348121,"uid":53498,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"同契哥蛾狗買？"},{"pid":"e990a093b180a49d595f37e334540bcf83c4bd8c","tid":2348121,"uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"上海夠話今日取代香港"},{"pid":"d64a173ccc2417adf924435b92c75f49f7b5435a","tid":2348121,"uid":64922,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"5nm晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901d462397c20cac2cdd23a6eaae61bc9c043110","tid":2348121,"uid":156121,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"快啦<br />\nbtw 你D貧鐵礦點燒都鍛唔出鋼材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36b489d09a4844be4bcdce2f02538a2cf4dbd23","tid":2348121,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":1